Package: multiflexi-database-connection
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, php-vitexsoftware-multiflexi-core, multiflexi-cli (>= 2.2.0)
Description: MultiFlexi Database Connection credential prototype
 PDO database connection credential prototype for MultiFlexi core.
 Provides the CredentialProtoType class that defines database driver,
 host, port, name, user and password configuration fields.

Package: multiflexi-database-connection-ui
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, multiflexi-database-connection (= ${binary:Version}), multiflexi-web
Description: MultiFlexi Database Connection UI components
 Database connection dialog for MultiFlexi web interface.
 Tests PDO connectivity, displays server version/driver info,
 and lists database tables.
